title: Flight Simulator 2020 - MSFS update - GOTY and Reno Races
description:
Asobo released Sim Update 6 yesterday. In addition to this they did announce both a new version of MSFS the Game of the Year (GOTY) Edition and a new addon the Reno Races. Both will be available on the 18th of November. The GOTY edition is a free update for everybody who already owns MSFS 2020 currently. The Reno Races addon will become available in two versions and will be a paid addon.
